> **Purpose of this file:** Master context for generating the Young Muslims (YM) Q2 2026 National
> Finance Report. Feed this file (plus the companion data files listed in §9) to Claude/an AI
> assistant when drafting the report. Anything marked `[DATA NEEDED]` or `[TBD]` must be filled
