## 7. Data Rules & Number Hygiene

- All figures come from the companion data files (§9) — **never invent or estimate numbers**. If a figure is missing, render `[PENDING]` visibly rather than guessing.
- Dollar amounts: whole dollars with commas ($12,450); use $ prefix always.
- Percentages: whole numbers unless precision matters (34%, not 34.17%).
- Income = green (`--green` / `--sys-green`), expenses = red (`--red`) — consistent with dashboard conventions.
- Pass-through amounts (e.g., YMC hotel/bus collections) must be labeled as pass-throughs so they don't inflate perceived program costs.
- FY2026 quarter definitions: `[CONFIRM: fiscal calendar — which months = Q2]`.

## 8. Style Guide (from NN Finance Handbook — match exactly)

Apple/iOS-inspired design system. Reuse these tokens verbatim:

```css
:root {
  /* Surfaces */
  --bg: #F2F2F7; --surface: #FFFFFF; --surface-2: #F2F2F7;
  /* Labels */
  --label: #1C1C1E; --label-2: #636366; --label-3: #AEAEB2;
  /* Separators */
  --sep: rgba(60,60,67,0.12); --sep-opaque: #E5E5EA;
  /* Brand */
  --green: #1A7A4A; --green-fill: rgba(26,122,74,0.10);
  --green-fill-strong: rgba(26,122,74,0.18);
  --gold: #C28A2A; --gold-fill: rgba(194,138,42,0.10);
  /* System semantic */
  --red: #FF3B30; --red-fill: rgba(255,59,48,0.09);
  --sys-green: #34C759; --sys-green-fill: rgba(52,199,89,0.10);
  --blue: #007AFF; --blue-fill: rgba(0,122,255,0.09);
  --orange: #FF9500; --orange-fill: rgba(255,149,0,0.10);
  /* Shadows */
  --s1: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.06), 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  --s2: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08), 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  --s3: 0 8px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.09), 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  /* Radius */
  --r1: 8px; --r2: 12px; --r3: 16px; --r4: 20px;
}
```

- **Fonts:** Headings: `-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif`; body: same stack with `'SF Pro Text'`.
- **Layout patterns to reuse from the handbook:** numbered section badges (01, 02…), white rounded cards on the `--bg` gray canvas, definition-list stat rows, green/gold pill badges, warning callouts (red-fill for strict rules, gold-fill for featured highlights, blue-fill for informational notes), clean tables with `--sep` row dividers.
- **Brand green** (`#1A7A4A`) is the primary accent; **gold** (`#C28A2A`) for highlights/quotes; system red/green only for financial semantics (expense/income).
- Bismillah SVG asset: `https://sulphia-iqbal.github.io/neighbornet-finances-handbook/bismillah.svg`
- **Print/PDF additions:** `@media print` — remove nav, force `page-break-before` on numbered sections, avoid breaking inside cards (`break-inside: avoid`), US Letter, ~0.5in margins, ensure backgrounds print (`print-color-adjust: exact`).

